uk.ac.glasgow.internman

Interface Visit

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    VisitImpl

    public interface Visit
    Each Software-Engineering student has to have an internship. Their performance is assessed by a visitor going to their place of work. This records the visit and associated grade.
    Author:
    TeamW
